ockquote><blockquote>有無諗過去工聯會試下係咪真係有興趣先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工聯會好？</blockquote><br />\n我意思係試下有無興趣先，唔洗用咁多錢出去讀，讀讀下發覺唔鐘意就死火姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過小心工聯會會趕客, 原本應該會令你鍾意都搞到你唔鍾意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係的確係方法之一, 當初我工聯會上左五堂俄文就轉會正式學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457d6084cbd334c6bfdbd8ff0e22e89229fb5f4b","tid":272862,"uid":66168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"好啦 咁我去工聯會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該曬"},{"pid":"b2afe8530b75d5d50778b8d2d603c26c015ce067","tid":272862,"uid":31898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好啦 咁我去工聯會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該曬</blockquote><br />\n老師質素參差，有個姓蕭嘅唔錯，作為過來人介紹返。"},{"pid":"7d6870aed0be1618c43f6fb2cb99a18b3411df02","tid":272862,"uid":66168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"想問工聯會啲老師係咪全部都係香港人？"},{"pid":"1d9402a7d1e781ed6f1f2aef2a3c75d50b8209c3","tid":272862,"uid":66168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Space 好似有得讀</blockquote><br />\nok 我問下先"},{"pid":"5761edf58745dbc591489650e385cfadaa625e0b","tid":272862,"uid":54377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"想學法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又去睇睇先"},{"pid":"2a0b40f3f7ded64b01581374dc5090210fbc7bcf","tid":272862,"uid":31898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問工聯會啲老師係咪全部都係香港人？</blockquote><br />\n唔係，有南美人"}]}